direction: right

*.style.border-radius: 8
*.style.font-size: 13
*.style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
*.style.stroke: "#333333"

# --- Entry ---

entry: |md
  **test-plan.analyze.endpoints**
  forked sub-agent

  - strategy files
  - ADR files (optional)
  - additional docs
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Scope ---

scope: |md
  **Extract Feature Scope**
  LLM analysis

  - purpose (WHAT/WHY/HOW)
  - in-scope items (from strategy)
  - out-of-scope (explicit only)
  - 3-7 test objectives
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- Endpoints ---

endpoints: |md
  **Extract Endpoints**
  LLM analysis

  - REST, gRPC, CLI, UI, Config
  - anti-hallucination rules
  - assign P0/P1/P2 priority
  - flag pending details
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- Output ---

output: |md
  **Structured Output**

  - Scope Analysis (Sec 1)
  - Endpoints table (Sec 4)
  - Gaps list
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Edges ---

entry -> scope
scope -> endpoints
endpoints -> output
